snippet.title: BLACK CASTLE: a new Game Boy platform game with monsters and knights (GB) 5MG
snippet.description:
Download free and more: https://www.5mgsite.com/post/black-castle-a-new-game-boy-game-with-monsters-and-knights-gb

Black Castle is a platform game for Game Boy where you control a knight who must defeat monsters inside a large castle. The game is inspired by games like Castlevania and Fortress of War.

- Buy a 5MG Channel a coffee for support: https://ko-fi.com/5mgchannel
- 5mg Site: http://www.5mgsite.com

Subscribe the channel, thumbs up the video, share it with your friends and visit our website.

Note¹: This is not a guide, but my experience playing games, sometimes, for the first time.
Note²: Please, Consider support us on: https://www.patreon.com/5minutesgameplay
